text: Wansbeck by-election may refer to one of three parliamentary by-elections held in the British House of Commons constituency of Wansbeck in Northumberland: *1918 Wansbeck by-election *1929 Wansbeck by-election *1940 Wansbeck by- election ;See also *Wansbeck (UK Parliament constituency)
title: Wansbeck by-election
